data.description: Beautiful Three Bedroom Brick Transitional built on two lots in Country Club Forest. Oak laid hardwoods and tiled floors throughout. Vaulted ceiling Family room with brick fireplace, multiple french doors open onto large masonry porch with fenced back yard. Split floor plan with large Owner's Bedroom, bath with tiled walk-in shower, free standing tub, massive walk-in closet with organizers. Granite countertops in eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances. On demand hot water. Covered porch connecting brick garage. Detached storage building adjacent to concrete driveway. Lot fronts State Maintained Rd. Landscaped partially open Hardwood lot only minutes from Roxboro.
